1. *Sama* sam sebi dovoljna. (I am enough for myself.)
2. Ona je *samo* sebi dala obećanje. (She only made a promise to herself.)
3. *Samo* ona zna istinu. (Only she knows the truth.)
4. *Sama* će sebi rešiti svoje probleme. (She will solve her own problems by herself.)
5. Ona je *sama* otišla u park. (She went to the park alone.)